&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Do you love the moment an idea becomes something you can click on? Do you enjoy sitting with the people who&#39;ll actually use what you make? Are you the kind of builder who can&#39;t quite tell where design ends and code begins - and likes it that way?&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;For our Copenhagen office, we are looking for an AI Product Developer to help us design, prototype, and build the next generation of data- and AI-driven products for our clients. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;This is not a traditional UX&amp;nbsp;designer&amp;nbsp;role, and&amp;nbsp;it&#39;s&amp;nbsp;not a traditional front-end role either.&amp;nbsp;It&#39;s&amp;nbsp;a builder role for someone who lives at the intersection of product thinking, design craft, front-end engineering, and emerging AI tools.&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;Who is Intellishore?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;Founded in 2013,&amp;nbsp;Intellishore&amp;nbsp;is home to 80+ passionate specialists in strategy, AI, and data, working from our Copenhagen and Zurich offices. We partner with leading organizations to shape the future of health, working with partners across the ecosystem to unlock the full potential of data and AI. Read more about our vision for Health 3.0 here: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.intellishore.dk/health&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;https://www.intellishore.dk/health&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;We are builders who believe in an open and honest approach to consulting. We ask questions, stand by our beliefs, and cut through complexity to create clarity. For us, progress&amp;nbsp;doesn’t&amp;nbsp;come from technology alone - it happens when the right people have the right data, strategy, and tools to act. As a collective of developers and strategists,&amp;nbsp;visionaries&amp;nbsp;and pragmatists, we bring energy,&amp;nbsp;expertise, and a passion for helping others succeed. Read more about our team here: &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.intellishore.dk/about&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;https://www.intellishore.dk/about.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;What will you be working on?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;none&quot;&gt;You’ll be working closely with our strategy and AI teams, turning strategies, models, and&amp;nbsp;new workflows into products that our clients actually use.&amp;nbsp;The role spans the full path from problem to shipped product:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:276}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-leveltext=&quot;&quot; data-font=&quot;Symbol&quot; data-listid=&quot;4&quot; data-list-defn-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;335552541&amp;quot;:1,&amp;quot;335559685&amp;quot;:720,&amp;quot;335559991&amp;quot;:360,&amp;quot;469769226&amp;quot;:&amp

&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The problem we&#39;re hiring you to solve&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Commercial pharma is sitting on a measurement problem. Launch decisions, field force deployment, HCP engagement, pricing - most of the value moves before anyone knows what worked, and the standard playbooks weren&#39;t built for fragmented channels, privacy constraints, or the causal questions that actually matter to commercial leaders. And the ground keeps moving - AI is rewriting what &quot;analytics&quot; even means to a commercial org, and the regulatory and tech stack underneath it all is shifting faster than most teams can absorb.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Intellishore works at the sharp end of this. Our commercial pharma practice partners with global top-20 pharma pioneers on data and AI decisions that shape launches, portfolios, and commercial performance. We&#39;re hiring a Principal Data Scientist to lead the technical depth of this work — shaping methodology, owning delivery on our most demanding engagements, and building out how we deliver measurements, causal inference, and machine learning in the next generation of our offerings.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you&#39;ll actually do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead the data science workstream on senior client engagements - typically 1-2 concurrent projects, working directly with client executives and brand leadership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set the technical bar on machine learning and forecasting across our commercial pharma portfolio and build the methods and templates that scale across the practice and into new segments.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mentor and grow a small team of data scientists and engineers. Team size: 10 today, growing to 30.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Shape new offerings alongside our leadership - from scoping to pricing to the IP that underpins them.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent Intellishore externally: Thought leadership, conferences, and senior client conversations where credibility matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who you are&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Must-haves:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;8+ years in data science, with meaningful time spent on machine learning and forecasting in commercial, marketing, or pricing contexts.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Track record of leading senior client-facing engagements or business-critical internal programs - consulting, in-house commercial analytics, or both.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong domain grounding in pharma, healthcare, or another regulated industry where commercial measurement is hard.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nice to have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Understanding MLOps at a level where you know what good looks like and can still get your hands dirty when it matters.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience shaping or launching data/AI offerings, practices, or products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Danish is a plus, not a requirement. Our working language is English.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why Intellishore?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re a boutique of ~100 people across Copenhagen and Zürich, and our commercial pharma stronghold is genuine - not a side bet. That means three things that matter at your level:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Real mandate.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;You&#39;ll own the technical direction of a practice, not a single workstream within a larger machine. If you&#39;ve wanted to shape how a firm approaches machine learning in healthcare, this is the seat.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Concrete path.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;Practice Lead for ML in Commercial Pharma within 1–2 years; Director track over 2–4 years from hire. We&#39;ll map it to your ambitions in the first conversation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Compensation.&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;We&#39;ll be direct about level, bonus structure, and the full package early in the process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;str

&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced consultant with proven experience driving data &amp;amp; AI projects, ideally within the pharma or other life science industries. Specifically, we are seeking a Senior Consultant to join our fast-growing Copenhagen office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Are you our new Senior Consultant?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you want to be part of an exciting journey where you will get plenty of responsibility and influence?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced consulting candidate who wants to drive and execute projects within data &amp;amp; AI. As a Senior Consultant, you will own work streams or entire projects, working closely with clients and technical colleagues. You&#39;ll be setting the agenda for our clients playing a pivotal role in every delivery. No project is the same, energy is high and you have a dynamic work week ahead of you.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our projects can be everything from actionable data and AI strategies, data architecture designs to advanced AI/ML models and scalable enterprise data platforms. Flexible and collaborative, we&#39;re not bound to any single technology or framework. You can read about some of our cases here:&amp;nbsp;&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.intellishore.dk/cases&quot;&gt;https://www.intellishore.dk/cases.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Our organization is structured around two tribes, Strategy &amp;amp; Transformation and AI &amp;amp; Engineering, working hand in hand on every project. We cross-staff dynamically, assembling cross-functional teams tailored to each project&#39;s needs. You&#39;ll be based in the Strategy &amp;amp; Transformation tribe.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Development is at the core of Intellishore, and we have dedicated plans for each Intellishorian and internal academy sessions for upskilling and knowledge sharing. You will also get the opportunity to influence and drive the business development of Intellishore to ensure we keep getting better at delivering value to our clients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;texttwo-module__description&quot;&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What are we looking for in a Senior Consultant?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking for an experienced individual with the competencies and professional mindset to lead strategic &amp;amp; technical projects within the health industry. More specifically, we hope that you have:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A proven track record for driving technology, data or AI projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience working with clients in the health industry (life sciences, pharma, medtech etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong problem solving skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proven experience in strategic advisory and project management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Natural flair for relation-building and stakeholder management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Energetic, outgoing, and ambitious personality with strong communication skills&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;And do not worry about whether you have too much or too little experience. We are always looking for curious and passionate people to join our family, and your title will be matched your level of seniority and expertise.&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
